		}
		{
			dependencies: ["EA000002"]
			description: [
				"§7§oA powerful yet destructive artifact; the Piglins swore to protect it at the cost of their lives.§r"
				""
				"§cPiglin Brutes§r guard the bastions of the Nether with golden axes and no fear. They cannot be distracted by gold and will not bargain."
				""
				"Defeat three of them to claim what they were sworn to keep."
			]
