			y: -6.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["EA000002"]
			description: [
				"§7§oHas witnessed destruction. Maybe it also witnessed your stuff disappear.§r"
				""
				"This eye has watched the end of countless things. Claim it by defeating the Wither \u2014 the very embodiment of wanton destruction."
				""
				"Summon the Wither by placing three §4Wither Skeleton Skulls§r on §8Soul Sand§r or §8Soul Soil§r in a T-shape. Then survive what comes next."
			]
