		{
			dependencies: ["EA000002"]
			description: [
				"§7§oRemembrance of the past lives of those who live in death.§r"
				""
				"§8Wither Skeletons§r carry memory of every soul they've ended. They roam Nether Fortresses in packs and inflict the Wither effect on hit."
				""
				"Bring Milk Buckets. Hunt 20 of them to uncover what they collectively remember."
