			description: [
				"§7§oThose who followed this eye were never seen again; rumors say they found the great city of Atlantis, or lost their way trying.§r"
				""
				"The §bElder Guardian§r rules the heart of each Ocean Monument. Three chambers, one Elder Guardian each. It inflicts Mining Fatigue and hits hard in open water."
				""
				"You only need to slay one. Whether you drain the monument or dive straight in is your call."
